metadata.name: daydreaming gets so hard #1/4
metadata.description: GOZDE focuses on the hypocrisy of society, speciesism, femininity, fears and leading crises such as inequality, violence and the environment. She has been an active member of the CryptoArt movement for two years and she supports the Dark Art movement in the NFT space. She tells her story through iconic characters and uses colors to induce emotions and create dark experiences. Her inspiration comes from contemporary society.
